::CyberShark/Magmatron::

    He cloaked and went inside the base, he was a=
stounded that it was whole again. He walked through the corridors and into =
a science lab. There he decloaked. He entered information about what he nee=
ded. Then he sent the information to another lab. There it started to build=
 the body.
    Magmatron became aware of this and looked in on it directly.=
 Once in the lab he watched as CyberShark completed the body. It was going =
to be quite impressive.

    CyberShark opened his chest plate over the bod=
y. His Spark and memories went into the body. Then the old CyberShark slump=
ed over. The New bot awoke, got up and let out a hiss. It crawled onto the =
celing and started for the door. The Door wouldn't open, so the bot let loo=
se it's tail. Like a whip the tail struck and the door fell.
    The Creatu=
re dropped in front of Magmatron. It rose to it's full height, which was ab=
out 6 foot 5 inches. it was still dwarfed by Magmatron, who was about 11 fe=
et tall.
    Then the bot transformed. It became a 8 foot tall killing mach=
ine, not that it wasn't a killing machine already, now he was bigger.
    "=
Magmatron," He said. "I figured the base was resulting in your return."
   =
 "Yes, CyberShark it was," Magmatron said.
    "Well, I was wondering if I =
could get some weapons," He looked at him evily. "I want to go on a Hunting=
 party."
    "Yes, well of course," Magmatron said, leading his puppet to t=
he weapon room. He supplied him with what he wanted. Then the new bot left.=

    "Ohh, by the way," He said cloaking. "The name's Dachande."
    Then h=
e left fully cloaked.
